xamples-10","page_id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples#quick-start","content":"The most basic possible usage:"},"389":{"id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples-11","page_id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples#quick-start","content":"colors are given to make the slices visible, but are not required, though\r\nwithout color or stroke colors you'll likely end up with just a circle\r\nvisually!{' '}"},"390":{"id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples-12","page_id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples#quick-start","content":"Of course it works with different data points too:"},"391":{"id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples-13","page_id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples#label-options","content":"You can use any string for the `labels` option, and they will be placed in the center of each pie slice."},"392":{"id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples-14","page_id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples#label-options","content":"Coloring is done via `labelColors`, which takes an array of colors that correspond to the labels. If not provided, the labels will default to white."},"393":{"id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples-15","page_id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples#data-labels","content":"Or you can use the `dataLabels` option to show the data values instead of custom labels:"},"394":{"id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples-16","page_id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples#data-labels","content":"`labelColors` also is used to color `dataLabels`.{' '}"},"395":{"id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples-17","page_id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples#data-labels","content":"The `dataLabels` option also accept `\"percentage\"`:"},"396":{"id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples-18","page_id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples#center-label","content":"The `centerLabel` option allows you to place a label in the center of the pie chart, which can be used to show a title or other value."},"397":{"id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples-19","page_id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples#center-label","content":"If you set the `centerLabel` option to `\"sum\"` the center label will show the sum of the data values:"},"398":{"id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples-20","page_id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples#center-label","content":"**Adjusting center label styles**"},"399":{"id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples-21","page_id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples#center-label","content":"There are a couple options that allow for adjustment of common title text styles for the center label."},"400":{"id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples-22","page_id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples#center-label","content":"`centerLabelFontSize`"},"401":{"id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples-23","page_id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples#center-label","content":"defaults to `32`"},"402":{"id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples-24","page_id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples#center-label","content":"`centerLabelFontWeight`"},"403":{"id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples-25","page_id":"/docs/examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"